    </td>
   </tr>
   <tr>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">RIG-I</td>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">Detects dsRNA and 5′- triphosphates of the negative ssRNA IAV genome, leading to innate immune responses activation.</td>
    <td align="center" valign="middle" style="border-bottom:solid thin" rowspan="1" colspan="1">rs72710678; R71H (NonSyn).
